Barrierdo

  • Zero 669
  • Feb 7, 2024
  • 1 min read

Name: Barrierdo


Availability: Legendary


Region: Forest


Preparation: Eating


Cost: N/A


Description: Upon taking one bit from the fruit, the rest of the fruit vanishes, and the user gains a new ability; this makes it so the user can not gain an ability from another fruit of a similar nature and is unable to touch purified water. This fruit grants the ability to create and manipulate a semi-transparent barrier at will.
